    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. The CFD hemolysis model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the COU decision regarding worst-case operating condition identification for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 criterion is satisfied at all 5 operating points. The assessment team accepts the model predictions as credible evidence for the 510(k) predicate comparison.",
